OL,3,CP&O Ferries: Angry scenes from unions
OL,4,Cat protests amid calls for action
OL,6,FThere were angry scenes outside
OL,7,FParliament today as former P&O staff
OL,8,Fand unions called for more to be done,
OL,9,Ftwo years after hundreds of crew
OL,10,Fmembers were sacked - and replaced
OL,11,Fwith cheaper agency staff.
OL,13,FUnions including the TUC and Nautilus
OL,14,Fjoined a demonstration outside
OL,15,FParliament.
OL,17,FThe Government insists legislation is
OL,18,Fon the way to stop anything similar
OL,19,Fhappening again.
