OL,4,Cat protests amid calls for action
OL,6,FBut after an ITV investigation found
OL,7,Fsome workers on the Dover to Calais
OL,8,Froute earn an average of less than #5p/
OL,9,Fh - critics say the company 'should be
OL,10,Fpenalised'.
OL,12,FSpeaking at the demonstration today,
OL,13,Fdirector of organising at Nautilus
OL,14,FInternational Martin Gray said: "The
OL,15,Fgovernment made a commitment through a
OL,16,Fnine-point plan in March of 2022, and
OL,17,Fso far they've delivered on none of it.
