OL,3,CP&O Ferries: Angry scenes from unions
OL,4,Cat protests amid calls for action
OL,6,F"We've got a code of practice that's
OL,7,Fnot fit for purpose, that just makes
OL,8,Fit marginally more expensive for
OL,9,Fcompanies to choose to ignore
OL,10,Fconsultation.
OL,12,F"And we've got a Seafarers Wages Act
OL,13,Fwith no legislation that backs it up
OL,14,Fin regulations."
OL,16,F"The government needs to go far enough
OL,17,Fto stop bad operators like P&O Ferries
OL,18,Ffrom being able to undertake the
OL,19,Femployment model that they do," he
OL,20,Fadded.
