OL,3,CP&O Ferries: Angry scenes from unions
OL,4,Cat protests amid calls for action
OL,6,F"It's a disgrace that seafarers are
OL,7,Fbeing paid as little as #4.85 an hour
OL,8,Fworking on-board ferries that are
OL,9,Foperating between the UK and France.
OL,11,F"Hundreds of the seafarers that were
OL,12,Fimpacted lived and worked in and
OL,13,Faround the Dover community - to remove
OL,14,Fthat many jobs from the local market
OL,15,Fin one fell swoop by the actions of a
OL,16,Fcompany is absolutely devastating for
OL,17,Ffamilies and for everybody else
OL,18,Finvolved.
