OL,3,CP&O Ferries: Angry scenes from unions
OL,4,Cat protests amid calls for action
OL,6,F"786 people lost their jobs in one
OL,7,Ffell swoop with no notice and no
OL,8,Fconsultation - that's 786 families
OL,9,Fwith no clue as to where the
OL,10,Fpaycheque's coming in from, how
OL,11,Fthey're going to pay the mortgage, how
OL,12,Fthey're going to pay the bills, how
OL,13,Fthey're going to afford to buy food in
OL,14,Fthe supermarkets."
OL,16,FP&O made significant cuts to staff in
OL,17,F2022, saying it was losing #100million
OL,18,Fyear on year, which forced it to make
OL,19,F'swift and significant changes'.
OL,21,FStaff were replaced by agency workers,
