OL,3,CP&O Ferries: Angry scenes from unions
OL,4,Cat protests amid calls for action
OL,6,FSeafarers were given immediate
OL,7,Fseverance notices on Thursday 17 March
OL,8,F2022.
OL,10,FBut the RMT are warning another P&O
OL,11,FFerries scandal is on the cards as a
OL,12,Fresult of government inaction.
OL,14,FLee Dempsey, senior assistant general
OL,15,Fsecretary of the RMT said: "Two years
OL,16,Fago, 800 of our members were sacked
OL,17,Fvia Zoom on vessels, and then some of
OL,18,Fthem were dragged off of those vessels
OL,19,Fby private security.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
