OL,3,CP&O Ferries: Angry scenes from unions
OL,4,Cat protests amid calls for action
OL,6,F"The employers, nothing happened to
OL,7,Fthem, P&O, have still not faced any
OL,8,Fsanctions or charges.
OL,10,F"The government has done nothing in
OL,11,Ftwo years.
OL,13,F"We could have another P&O tomorrow -
OL,14,Fwe still have thousands of seafarers
OL,15,Fin British waters who are paid below
OL,16,Fthe minimum wage, who don't have any
OL,17,Fpension provisions, and could face
OL,18,Fbeing dismissed in the same way that
OL,19,Four members were two years ago."
