OL,3,CP&O Ferries: Angry scenes from unions
OL,4,Cat protests amid calls for action
OL,6,FNatalie Elphicke, the MP for Dover and
OL,7,FDeal says the Seafarers' Wages Act is
OL,8,Fmaking sure that pay conditions are in
OL,9,Fplace to protect seafarers in the same
OL,10,Fway that people are protected on land.
OL,12,F"There is a new code which DFDS and
OL,13,FP&O have agreed to implement, dealing
OL,14,Fwith those welfare and other
OL,15,Fconditions, to make sure our seafarers
OL,16,Fare properly looked after," she told
OL,17,FITV Meridian.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
