OL,3,CP&O Ferries: Angry scenes from unions
OL,4,Cat protests amid calls for action
OL,6,F"It's absolutely vital that that
OL,7,Fbecomes compulsory, and that's what I
OL,8,Fwant to see, to make sure our
OL,9,Fseafarers are properly looked after on
OL,10,Four cross-Channel route.
OL,12,F"There continue to be discussions with
OL,13,FFrance about making sure that
OL,14,Fseafarers are properly protected on
OL,15,Four cross-Channel route.
OL,17,F"I'm very pleased that progress has
OL,18,Fbeen made since the disgraceful
OL,19,Fepisode two years ago, but I support
OL,20,Fmuch more happening as well."
